file_content.text: Hmm. The upload has stopped. But the algorithm was flawless. Someone must be interfering with the upload manually.
When I find out who, they'll die.
The interference is coming from within the lab.
I haven't seen any sign of the Republic or the Balmorran resistance in here.
We should keep all possibilities open.
The interference is coming from deeper inside the lab. I hate to ask it of you, but I need the rest of that data.
Keep on your guard. Anyone with the ability to get into that lab is very dangerous.
